questions.question:
Thank you for your interest in applying to fundraise with USEED! To get the process rolling, we would like to collect some information about you and your crowdfunding idea. This process will take about 10-15 minutes to complete.

Upon submission, our team will review and assess your application. Please take your time as your application will help us evaluate your suitability for the program.

If your application meets our program criteria, a USEED Coach will follow up to schedule a virtual interview session with you and anyone else you feel should attend. 

If at any point you have questions, please do not hesitate to reach out to support@useed.org.
Please write your name below.
